  <title>Gio.TlsRehandshakeMode</title>
  <p>When to allow rehandshaking. See
<link xref="Gio.TlsConnection.set_rehandshake_mode"/>.</p>
  <p>Since 2.28</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>TlsRehandshakeMode.NEVER</code></title>
  <p>Never allow rehandshaking</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>TlsRehandshakeMode.SAFELY</code></title>
  <p>Allow safe rehandshaking only</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>TlsRehandshakeMode.UNSAFELY</code></title>
  <p>Allow unsafe rehandshaking</p>
</item>
